narinig ang tungkol sa kanyang mga kwento.

507
00:37:45,679 --> 00:37:47,000
Sige na at magpakilala ka na.

508
00:37:47,559 --> 00:37:48,599
Kumusta, ako si Xing Wu.

509
00:37:53,039 --> 00:37:53,639
Iyon lang?

510
00:37:54,079 --> 00:37:54,719
Iyon lang.

511
00:37:56,239 --> 00:37:57,599
Sige, tigil-tigilan mo ang ingay.

512
00:37:58,760 --> 00:37:59,519
Wala pang
isang taon ang natitira sa atin

513
00:38:00,679 --> 00:38:01,400
para maghanda para sa gaokao.

514
00:38:01,840 --> 00:38:03,119
Gusto ko kayong lahat

515
00:38:03,320 --> 00:38:05,239
para matuto mula sa isa't isa at magkasundo.

516
00:38:05,840 --> 00:38:06,400
Xing Wu,

517
00:38:06,760 --> 00:38:07,880
umupo ka sa bakanteng upuan na iyon.

518
00:38:10,039 --> 00:38:11,239
Sige, simula na ng klase.

519
00:38:16,760 --> 00:38:19,360
Lumiko sa pahina pito.

520
00:38:20,159 --> 00:38:21,599
Bumalik nang walang paalam?

521
00:38:27,599 --> 00:38:28,360
[Maligayang pagbabalik.]

522
00:38:29,719 --> 00:38:31,239
[Lahat ay mausisa]

523
00:38:31,599 --> 00:38:33,199
[bakit bigla kang nagbago ng isip]

524
00:38:33,199 --> 00:38:33,840
[at bumalik na sa paaralan.]

525
00:38:33,840 --> 00:38:35,320
Pagsusuri ng tungkulin

526
00:38:35,320 --> 00:38:37,320
at mga aplikasyong hinango.

527
00:38:37,840 --> 00:38:38,800
Tingnan
ang problemang ito

528
00:38:39,880 --> 00:38:41,599
at pag-isipang mabuti ang solusyon.

529
00:38:41,599 --> 00:38:42,639
Tanungin mo ako kung natigil ka.

530
00:38:51,880 --> 00:38:53,000
Para lang makakuha ng diploma sa hayskul.

531
00:39:00,480 --> 00:39:01,239
Alam mo ba?

532
00:39:01,480 --> 00:39:02,760
Kasama sa klase namin si Xing Wu.

533
00:39:03,320 --> 00:39:03,880
Xing Wu?

534
00:39:04,199 --> 00:39:05,599
Hindi mo siya kilala?

535
00:39:05,840 --> 00:39:06,920
Narinig ko ang tungkol sa

536
00:39:06,920 --> 00:39:07,840
ang daming tsismis tungkol sa kanya.

537
00:39:08,159 --> 00:39:09,320
Makita siya nang personal,

538
00:39:09,480 --> 00:39:11,559
Para siyang isang tunay na bida sa pelikula!

539
00:39:11,960 --> 00:39:12,599
Mababaw.

540
00:39:12,760 --> 00:39:13,920
Hindi lang siya basta gwapo,

541
00:39:14,320 --> 00:39:15,039
ngunit gayundin

542
00:39:16,199 --> 00:39:17,320
napaka-lalaki.

543
00:39:20,000 --> 00:39:22,159
At may mainit akong balita.

544
00:39:22,880 --> 00:39:24,440
Sina Qing Ye at Xing Wu

545
00:39:24,960 --> 00:39:26,519
magpinsan talaga sila.

546
00:39:26,960 --> 00:39:28,000
Alam ko na.

547
00:39:28,800 --> 00:39:29,880
Bakit wala akong

548
00:39:29,960 --> 00:39:31,519
pinsan na ganyan?

549
00:39:31,679 --> 00:39:32,920
Huwag mong sabihing gusto mo siya.

550
00:39:33,159 --> 00:39:34,239
Siyempre ginagawa ko.

551
00:39:34,559 --> 00:39:36,079
Gwapo siya,

552
00:39:36,079 --> 00:39:37,159
Naglalaro siya ng basketball,

553
00:39:37,239 --> 00:39:38,639
at pinoprotektahan ang kanyang kapatid na babae.

554
00:39:38,800 --> 00:39:40,239
Talagang tipo ko.

555
00:39:40,480 --> 00:39:41,199
Parang isang taong
galing sa isang drama.

556
00:39:42,320 --> 00:39:43,000
Hindi ba sa tingin mo?

557
00:39:43,559 --> 00:39:44,360
Hindi ko ginagawa.

558
00:39:44,800 --> 00:39:46,039
Na-expelled na siya dati.

559
00:39:46,159 --> 00:39:47,239
Ano ba ang magugustuhan?

560
00:39:47,480 --> 00:39:48,519
Hindi!

561
00:39:48,519 --> 00:39:49,320
Nabalitaan kong dati siyang

562
00:39:49,320 --> 00:39:50,519
magkaroon ng magagandang grado!

563
00:39:50,840 --> 00:39:52,000
Binu-bully siya ng mga tulisan

564
00:39:52,039 --> 00:39:53,159
at pinarusahan dahil dito.

565
00:39:53,199 --> 00:39:54,519
Siya mismo ang nagbakasyon.

566
00:40:00,440 --> 00:40:01,519
Salamat, Ginoong Zhu.

567
00:40:01,599 --> 00:40:02,039
Walang problema.
Liu Nian!

568
00:40:03,199 --> 00:40:04,119
Tulungan mo ako sa mga gamit!

569
00:40:04,239 --> 00:40:05,079
Paparating na!

570
00:40:05,440 --> 00:40:05,960
Nakuha ko na.
- Ito na.
- Ginoong Zhu.

571
00:40:06,960 --> 00:40:08,079
- Ginoong Zhu.
- Hayaan mo na.

572
00:40:08,199 --> 00:40:08,639
Oo.
Sige.

573
00:40:09,480 --> 00:40:10,599
Alam na alam ni Liu Nian.

574
00:40:11,119 --> 00:40:12,440
Pinahahalagahan ko talaga, Ginoong Zhu.

575
00:40:12,639 --> 00:40:13,559
Hinatid mo pa ako pabalik.

576
00:40:13,760 --> 00:40:14,119
Bueno,

577
00:40:14,199 --> 00:40:15,480
Masaya lang ako na bumalik na si Xing Wu.

578
00:40:16,119 --> 00:40:17,119
Tungkol sa kanya,

579
00:40:17,320 --> 00:40:18,599
May utang na loob talaga ako sa'yo.

580
00:40:18,639 --> 00:40:19,960
Kung wala ang iyong tulong,

581
00:40:20,000 --> 00:40:21,559
hindi na sana siya nakabalik

582
00:40:21,599 --> 00:40:22,679
papunta sa klase nang maayos.

583
00:40:23,760 --> 00:40:24,519
Wala lang 'yan.
Huwag kang mag-alala.

584
00:40:26,159 --> 00:40:27,960
Naku, huwag mong sabihin 'yan.

585
00:40:28,480 --> 00:40:29,159
Ginoong Zhu,
kunin mo na ito.

586
00:40:30,400 --> 00:40:31,199
Isang voucher.
Hindi!

587
00:40:31,960 --> 00:40:33,840
Kunin mo na. Pumunta ka sa tindahan ko anumang oras,

588
00:40:33,920 --> 00:40:36,159
gupit, paghuhugas, pagkukulot,

589
00:40:36,159 --> 00:40:36,599
lahat may diskwento.
Sandali, Lanfang,

590
00:40:37,320 --> 00:40:38,239
Hindi madaling magpatakbo ng negosyo.
Hindi ko ito kayang tiisin.

591
00:40:38,920 --> 00:40:40,639
Pero lagi mo akong tinutulungan.

592
00:40:40,679 --> 00:40:42,000
Mas lalo lang sasama ang pakiramdam ko.

593
00:40:42,000 --> 00:40:43,000
Kunin mo na lang.

594
00:40:43,599 --> 00:40:44,639
Pumunta ka sa Isla ng Xuan anumang oras.

595
00:40:44,960 --> 00:40:45,320
Sige.
May klase ako mamaya,

596
00:40:46,239 --> 00:40:46,880
Babalik ako.
Sige.

597
00:40:47,440 --> 00:40:47,960
Salamat.

598
00:40:48,400 --> 00:40:49,079
Nakakuha siya ng voucher.

599
00:40:50,400 --> 00:40:51,239
Wala kaming nakuha!
Oo!

600
00:40:52,400 --> 00:40:52,960
Mag-ingat ka.
Paalam.

601
00:40:57,360 --> 00:40:59,679
Ang galing talaga ni Mr. Zhu!

602
00:40:59,920 --> 00:41:02,199
Hindi lang nakapagbalik kay Wu sa paaralan,

603
00:41:02,320 --> 00:41:03,519
nagmaneho pa nga siya

604
00:41:03,519 --> 00:41:04,679
ang aming tahanan sa Lanfang!

605
00:41:04,760 --> 00:41:06,760
Mga taong hindi nakakaalam

606
00:41:06,960 --> 00:41:07,880
iisipin niyang lalaki siya,

607
00:41:08,000 --> 00:41:09,199
hindi isang guro.

608
00:41:10,519 --> 00:41:11,880
Kayong dalawa.

609
00:41:12,159 --> 00:41:13,840
Enjoyin mo na lang ang pakwan mo.

610
00:41:14,039 --> 00:41:15,679
Kinakain na namin ang drama mo!

611
00:41:15,719 --> 00:41:16,320
Kami nga!
Meron din ako.

612
00:41:17,920 --> 00:41:18,880
Oo, meron ako.

613
00:41:22,679 --> 00:41:23,239
Masakit ang binti?

614
00:41:32,880 --> 00:41:34,079
Bakit mo ako kinurot?

615
00:41:34,719 --> 00:41:35,719
Gusto ko lang makita

616
00:41:36,599 --> 00:41:37,800
kung totoo ito.

617
00:41:38,199 --> 00:41:39,400
Parang hindi totoo.

618
00:41:39,880 --> 00:41:41,880
Naka-uniporme ka,

619
00:41:42,400 --> 00:41:43,360
at naglalakad na kami pauwi

620
00:41:43,400 --> 00:41:44,679
magkasama.

621
00:41:45,400 --> 00:41:47,320
Parang medyo surreal.

622
00:41:48,039 --> 00:41:48,920
Kung gayon dapat ba akong

623
00:41:49,280 --> 00:41:50,360
i-flick ang iyong noo

624
00:41:51,039 --> 00:41:52,719
