625
00:41:54,039 --> 00:41:54,760
Hindi,
ayos lang ako.

626
00:41:55,360 --> 00:41:56,559
Parang totoo na ngayon.

627
00:41:56,679 --> 00:41:57,360
Hindi panaginip.
Talagang hindi panaginip!

628
00:41:58,159 --> 00:41:58,960
Ako ito.

629
00:41:59,039 --> 00:42:00,199
Kailangan ko ng kumpirmasyon.

630
00:42:01,239 --> 00:42:02,199
Parang nananaginip ako.
Hindi ikaw.

631
00:42:03,119 --> 00:42:03,800
Mayroon akong…
- Subukan ko.
- kinumpirma ko.

632
00:42:04,639 --> 00:42:05,159
Hindi!

633
00:42:05,159 --> 00:42:06,320
Tingnan ko kung nananaginip lang ako.

634
00:42:06,480 --> 00:42:07,639
Anyway, hindi naman ako nananaginip.

635
00:42:18,519 --> 00:42:19,119
Gumising?

636
00:42:19,719 --> 00:42:20,320
Oo.

637
00:42:20,960 --> 00:42:21,760
Gising na gising.

638
00:42:26,000 --> 00:42:27,079
Sakay ka, bubuhatin kita.

639
00:42:30,679 --> 00:42:32,400
Ayos lang ako, kaya ko nang maglakad.

640
00:42:33,960 --> 00:42:35,199
Masyado kang mabagal,

641
00:42:35,400 --> 00:42:36,440
Mahuhuli tayo sa bus.

642
00:42:36,880 --> 00:42:37,440
Tara na.

643
00:42:50,119 --> 00:42:51,320
Kung ako'y masyadong mabigat,

644
00:42:51,480 --> 00:42:52,760
ibaba mo na lang ako.

645
00:42:54,440 --> 00:42:54,880
Ayos ka lang.

646
00:42:55,519 --> 00:42:57,239
Mas magaan pa kaysa sa lata ng gas at isdang-dagat.

647
00:42:59,840 --> 00:43:00,840
Nagkikimkim pa rin ng sama ng loob?

648
00:43:01,519 --> 00:43:02,639
Natatandaan ko lang nang mabuti ang mga bagay-bagay.

649
00:43:18,719 --> 00:43:19,360
Masakit ba ang noo mo?

650
00:43:39,320 --> 00:43:41,239
Salamat sa tulong ni G. Zhu,

651
00:43:42,039 --> 00:43:43,440
kinausap niya ang punong-guro

652
00:43:43,440 --> 00:43:44,199
at sinabing ikaw ay

653
00:43:44,199 --> 00:43:45,480
isang mag-aaral na may pangako.

654
00:43:45,960 --> 00:43:47,280
Kung hindi, babalik na sa paaralan

655
00:43:47,639 --> 00:43:48,719
